text:
Today, New Zealand officially has zero active COVID-19 cases 👏

Prime Minister Jacinda Ardern announced that, thanks to the hard work of our team of 5 million, we will move into Alert Level 1 from midnight tonight. https://t.co/IHYdnn1o2y
